      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "What you two share is an essential connection stripped of all pretense. You value the trust of communicating what needs to be said, when it needs to be said, over pleasantries and polished words. You are unafraid of silence and respect each other's solitude. The quiet certainty of \"I know\" brings a comfort that runs deeper than any words could."
