            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "What you two share is a deep aversion to superficial connections. You dislike empty pleasantries and would rather choose silence over hollow words. In return, the rare words you do exchange carry profound meaning. Because you only speak of what truly matters, you have built a rare kind of trust where every word is taken to heart."
