            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "What suits you two perfectly is \"play that leaves things to chance.\" Spinning a roulette wheel to pick your destination, watching a movie from a genre you’ve never tried, accidentally getting hooked on a hobby you started on a whim — the thrill of not knowing what’s next is what makes your relationship shine brightest. You’re the type whose best memories come from dates with zero plans."
