            "value" : "What suits you two perfectly is \"experiences that break the mold.\" An art workshop, an improvised cooking challenge, a walk with no destination, exploring quirky little shops — finding joy in \"things nobody else does\" is your true forte. The wilder the idea, the more fun you have. A creative, off-the-beaten-path approach to play is your perfect match."
