            "value" : "What fits you two best is \"activities that spark each other’s intellectual curiosity.\" Watching documentaries together, battling it out in board games, recommending books on new topics to each other — learning from each other’s perspectives is the greatest thrill of all. When a lively debate gets going, that’s your very own premium entertainment."
