          }
        }
      }
    },
    "二人の暗黙のルールは「型にはめない」こと。「カップルならこうするべき」という常識に縛られず、二人が心地よいと感じるスタイルを優先する。周りから見て変でも、二人がOKならOK。この自由さへの合意が、クリエイティブな関係を守る最強のルールです。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your unwritten rule is \"don't force it into a mold.\" You refuse to be bound by what couples are \"supposed\" to do, choosing instead whatever feels right for the two of you. Even if others think it's strange, if you're both okay with it, that's all that matters. This mutual agreement on freedom is the strongest rule protecting your creative relationship."
