    },
    "二人の暗黙のルールは「察してほしい、でも察しすぎない」こと。言葉にしなくても伝わっている安心感がある一方で、本当に大事なことは勇気を出して言葉にする。「言わなくてもわかる」と「ちゃんと言う」の絶妙なバランスが、この関係を支えるルールです。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your unwritten rule is \"read between the lines, but don't overread.\" There's a comforting sense that feelings come through even without words, yet when something truly matters, you find the courage to say it out loud. The exquisite balance between \"you just know\" and \"say it properly\" is the rule that sustains your relationship."
