    },
    "二人の暗黙のルールは「感情を我慢しない」こと。嬉しい時も怒っている時も、感じたままを相手にぶつける。取り繕わない生の感情が二人の絆。ただし「感情をぶつけた後は必ずフォローする」という後始末のルールも忘れずに。嵐の後の仲直りが、二人の関係を一番強くしてくれます。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your unwritten rule is \"don't bottle up your emotions.\" Whether happy or angry, you let each other feel the raw, unfiltered truth. That unpolished honesty is your bond. But you also never forget the follow-up rule: always make amends after an emotional outburst. It's the making up after the storm that makes your relationship the strongest it can be."
